org.codehaus.cargo.container.configuration.builder

Interface ConfigurationBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractConfigurationBuilder, AbstractTomcatConfigurationBuilder, JRun4xConfigurationBuilder, OrionConfigurationBuilder, Resin2xConfigurationBuilder, Resin3xConfigurationBuilder, Tomcat4xConfigurationBuilder, Tomcat5x6x7xConfigurationBuilder, Tomcat8x9xConfigurationBuilder, WebLogic8xConfigurationBuilder, WebLogic9x10x103x12xConfigurationBuilder

    public interface ConfigurationBuilder
    Builds String representations a Resource configuration. These may be JSON or XML or Properties that the Container will know what to do with.
